query:
UPDATE inventory 
SET tenantId = (SELECT id FROM tenants WHERE name LIKE '%Albert Einstein%' LIMIT 1)
WHERE id IN (
  SELECT i.id
  FROM inventory i
  JOIN warehouseLocations wl ON i.locationId = wl.id
  WHERE wl.code LIKE 'Z01-01-%'
);
